        "date": "1915-03-18",
        "eng": "Lovely letter from David yesterday! \u2014\u2014 Moved to the factory. Answered David. Very sensual.",
        "ger": "Gestern lieben Brief von David! \u2014\u2014 Bin in die Fabrik umgezogen. David geantwortet. Sehr sinnlich. "
